      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house solver, Ansys Mechanical 2022R2, DePuy Synthes proprietary solver) operate under documented software quality management plans including version control, regression test suites, and change-control procedures consistent with ISO 9001. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for this medium-risk COU."
