      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including cantilever beam bending, Hertzian contact, and bolt preload patch tests were executed in all three codes. Results agree with analytical solutions to within 0.5% for linear cases and 2.1% for nonlinear contact cases, confirming correct implementation of governing equations."
