      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Iterative solver convergence was monitored; force residuals below 1×10⁻⁴ N and displacement residuals below 1×10⁻⁶ mm were enforced for all load steps. Automated convergence checks are embedded in the run scripts. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
