      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry, grip constraints, and loading point locations. Fixture compliance was measured and incorporated into the model. Material properties and geometry used in FEA are matched to the specific test specimens via CMM and material certification data."
    },
    {
