      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric across all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm). All E/uval values below 1.96 acceptance threshold. Experimental uncertainty estimated from inter-laboratory variability and measurement system analysis. Graphical force-displacement curve overlay provided for qualitative confirmation. Achieved level 4 exceeds required level 3."
